data.text: @PokerPolitics Every fuxkin year is an election year, like literally , there is not a year where there are not elections 🙄

@PokerPolitics It's a pretty standard bit of silliness in conspiracy theories. The "Enemy" is always more powerful than God but can also be defeated easily by a scrappy group of rebels.
QANON takes it to a whole new level, though, where the Cabal rules everything but can't read Twitter.
@PokerPolitics Should have cut that deal with Hillary.
